    "name": "Lost in the Crowd",
    "prerequisite": "*Lion Blade Dedication*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You\u2019ve learned how to move as one with crowds and hide among them, vanishing into a busy street in the flicker of an eye. You move at full Speed in crowds and can use cover from crowds to Hide and Sneak, gaining a +2 circumstance bonus to your Stealth checks when in a crowd of at least 10 creatures and a +4 circumstance bonus to your Stealth checks when in a crowd of at least 100 creatures.",
